title: Packers: Received $432.6M in revenue sharing
description: The Packers, the NFL's only publicly owned team, revealed Wednesday that the national revenue sharing from the previous fiscal year was a record $432.6 million.
author: Rob Demovsky

title: Westwood slams rankings system as 'mockery'
description: Lee Westwood became the latest LIV Golf player to criticize the world golf ranking system, calling it a "mockery."

title: We meet again - England & Spain set for 'amazing' Euro 2025 final
description: Two years on from the World Cup final, England and Spain will meet again in what promises to be an "amazing" Euro 2025 final.

title: Dawson makes England a better side - Vaughan
description: England are a better side with veteran spinner Liam Dawson included, says former captain Michael Vaughan.

title: Wiegman: Kelly 'thrives on' producing England magic
description: Sarina Wiegman hailed Chloe Kelly for "thriving on" producing in the big moments after her 119th-minute goal sent England into the Euro 2025 final.

title: Manchester derby and Arsenal vs Man City live on Sky Sports in September
description: The Manchester derby and Man City's trip to Arsenal will be live on Sky Sports in September.

title: Kwan's go-ahead single in 8th sends surging Guardians to 3-2 win over Orioles
description: Steven Kwan singled home Bo Naylor with two outs in the eighth inning for the go-ahead run, lifting the Cleveland Guardians to a 3-2 victory over the Baltimore Orioles on Wednesday night. Naylor was on second base when Kwan lined a pitch from Colin Selby (0-2) into left field. Colton Cowser fielded it cleanly, but his throw to catcher Alex Jackson was well off the mark, allowing Naylor to score.
author: BRIAN DULIK

title: James Franklin predicts historic season for Penn State running back duo
description: Nicholas Singleton and Kaytron Allen are back for more in 2025, and James Franklin could not be happier about the situation.
